    Death Knight and Lich (only if I can make a water freezing visual effect)
    Demon Hunter?
    Sea Witch
    Pit Lord (will require a new model)
    
  SHIPS AND SHIPYARDS
  Invulnerable Neutral Goblin Shipyards are spread across the water, with Goblin Sloops for hire. 
  However, these also "sell" upgrades to itself into player-owned, vulnerable shipyard building for each race.
  Each race shipyard allows training unique ships, while also allowing allies to hire transport ships. Destroying a shipyard reverts it back to a neutral Goblin Shipyard instead 
  
  I might just change the names to generic ones such as "Transport Ship" and "Battleship"
  
